{"sequence":52,"timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:22:38.474388081Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-3-9c6f07f2","body":"Fix the final-review diagnostics to report the new reviewer defaults from `final_review.backends`. The compiled default panel now comes from `src/contexts/workspace_governance/config.rs:266-270`, but `src/contexts/agent_execution/diagnostics.rs:785-824` still renders the `final_reviewer` row by calling `resolve_role_target(FinalReviewer, 1)`, and `src/contexts/agent_execution/policy.rs:60-76` resolves that role through the planner-family fallback instead of the explicit final-review panel. In a clean workspace this produces a contradictory result: `backend show-effective --json` reports only `final_reviewer = claude/claude-opus-4-6`, while `backend probe --role final_review_panel --flow standard --json` correctly resolves the panel as `codex/gpt-5.4-xhigh` plus `claude/claude-opus-4-6`. Update `show-effective` (and singular `final_reviewer` probes if they remain supported via `src/contexts/agent_execution/diagnostics.rs:870-884`) to surface the actual `final_review.backends` members, or stop exposing a generic `final_reviewer` role that no longer matches runtime behavior.","dedup_key":"7fa21af1c217d52b4e22d263043274b7be7bf695a0b574d78ff4519b37812ce5","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"codex","model_id":"gpt-5.4-xhigh","reviewer_id":"reviewer-1"}],"run_id":"run-20260412172012","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
{"sequence":53,"timestamp":"2026-04-12T18:22:38.483655677Z","event_type":"amendment_queued","details":{"amendment_id":"fr-3-9c639dfb","body":"High: The current patch does not change backend-default implementation logic at all—it only updates live run state files, so the requested default-behavior changes are not actually implemented in code (`src/contexts/workspace_governance/config.rs` and `src/contexts/agent_execution/policy.rs` are unchanged). The diff adds only `.ralph-burning/projects/utm/journal.ndjson:35-43` and `.ralph-burning/projects/utm/run.json:16-73`.","dedup_key":"d21353fad9a1127c5cfd183bf503f7f02bac4c62cdac0d1f1a2e4c90912f41da","reviewer_sources":[{"backend_family":"claude","model_id":"claude-opus-4-6","reviewer_id":"reviewer-2"}],"run_id":"run-20260412172012","source":"workflow_stage","source_stage":"final_review"}}
